tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T34 at Q-School, earning conditional status. Made cuts in the three events he played with a T18 his best finish. Sat at T3 after 54 holes until a Sunday 73 derailed his momentum at the ATB Financial Classic in August.
tourBios.personal: Married in college...Favorite course he's played is Augusta National and wants to play Pine Valley...Favorite pro sports teams are the Atlanta Braves, Atlanta Falcons and Atlanta Hawks...Dream foursome would include Moe Norman, Tiger Woods and Seve Ballesteros.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T18th in 2015 at the ATB Financial Classic.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T29th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
